<!-- VALUE PROPOSITIONS -->
<section class="section value-section" id="value">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">What You Get</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Not just organized — operationally sharp.</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">
      Most EAs keep things tidy. I keep things running. Here's the difference you'll notice from week one.
    </p>

    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">🗓</span>
        <h3>Calendar & Inbox You Can Trust</h3>
        <p>Complex, multi-timezone scheduling across executive teams — with zero double-bookings, no missed priorities, and communications managed with complete discretion. You focus on the meeting; I handle everything before and after.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">✈️</span>
        <h3>Travel & Logistics, End-to-End</h3>
        <p>From itinerary planning to visa processing, I've coordinated travel for CEOs and Board Directors across international corridors. Arrangements that save money without sacrificing efficiency — proven track record with executives at multinational firms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">📁</span>
        <h3>Documentation That Stays Audit-Ready</h3>
        <p>Whether it's employment contracts, compliance records, or executive correspondence — documentation I manage is accurate, organized, and audit-proof. I achieved 100% documentation compliance across ISO audits with zero findings requiring corrective action.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">🤝</span>
        <h3>Vendor & Stakeholder Coordination</h3>
        <p>Experienced negotiating with staffing agencies, vendors, and subcontractors on behalf of leadership. I protect the organization's interests and keep agreements compliant, current, and clearly documented.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">🔒</span>
        <h3>Trusted With the Sensitive</h3>
        <p>Confidential data, personnel matters, executive communications — I've handled all of it across multinational environments where discretion wasn't optional. You'll never need to second-guess what's in safe hands.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <span class="value-icon">⚙️</span>
        <h3>SOP & Process Ownership</h3>
        <p>I don't just follow processes — I build and improve them. From QA-led systems to attendance tracking frameworks, I've redesigned workflows that gave leadership real-time visibility and cut ambiguity across teams.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

